{"tid":2449916,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"羅致光：僱主放無薪假是將工作分享避免裁員　冀互諒互讓","createTime":"2021-03-17T04:35:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T09:39:09.000Z","uid":20933,"like":4,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"61451cb2f1a194a8696bf4e8f5c78837200d1683","tid":2449916,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T04:35:14.000Z","msg":"在立法會上，勞工及福利局長羅致光被問到，政府多項支援措施都是針對失業人士，忽略就業不足的僱員，他表示，企業安排員工放無薪假，是將工作互相分享（Job Sharing），反映市場有靈活性，舉例指原本一星期工作5天的員工，如果沒有放1天無薪假，不將工作分享，僱主將可以解僱兩成人手。他表示，放無薪假固然影響收入，但他希望大家互諒互讓，總好過有人被裁走。 <br />\n<br />\n多名商界議員要求政府推出新一輪保就業計劃，自由黨鍾國斌批評，政府眼見最新失業率升至7.2%，是17年來新高，仍然無動於衷，是盲目。羅致光重申，政府早前已推出超過3000億元的紓困措施，財赤亦錄得新高，基於財政考慮，不會推出新一輪保就業計劃。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2383351\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2383351&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixRT9vY2lxR77dvs0GIZdErU%3D&h=f1795f2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2383351</a>"},{"pid":"2103f9876a4292c2b1e61068ceafe33f6c7af9ea","tid":2449916,"uid":258784,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T04:38:05.000Z","msg":"僱主拖欠薪金是防止公司倒閉避免裁員<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77fe79146beb2b462c7a01c5c4ad68555107cd66","tid":2449916,"uid":146535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T04:38:08.000Z","msg":"唔夠工返要分批返被佢講到係靈活性"},{"pid":"3f3420443855e7273bea3c191cfdba9b6d3acbfa","tid":2449916,"uid":293472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T04:39:14.000Z","msg":"放完無薪假再炒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f296f6afeab93f8e96a2f793533822bb24aaab4","tid":2449916,"uid":18753,"like"